      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for a new home! This car is an absolute gem\u2014it\u2019s been totally babied and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in pristine condition inside and out, with a sparkling finish and an interior that still has that fresh feel. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the full retail price tag, you've found it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a peek!",
