    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six independent throttle bodies. The Getrag Type D 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated M-Variable locking differential. Mechanically, this chassis is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for the platform. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping with zero bushing deflection. Cosmetically, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the Nappa leather interior shows no compression or bolster wear. This is a turnkey, collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
