    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and maintained to the highest standards. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing or bolster wear, while the original carpets have been shielded by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is peerless, boasting a comprehensive service history with all scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified specialists. There are zero leaks, no rattles, and the engine delivers crisp, effortless power paired with a smooth-shifting transmission. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
