    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive example of the A80 platform. This specimen retains its original 2JZ-GTE sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six, paired with the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The engine exhibits factory-spec compression across all cylinders, and the turbochargers spool with zero shaft play. Mechanical integrity is bolstered by a Torsen limited-slip differential and untouched double-wishbone suspension geometry. All VIN tags remain intact on factory panels, confirming an accident-free history. This is a collector-grade vehicle with zero modifications, offering the pure, unadulterated performance characteristics of the 90s JDM golden era.",
